snippet.title: Gumslinger - Trailer 3.0 - Mobile Game (iOS/Android)
snippet.description:
Get Gumslinger on App Store and Google Play: https://gumslinger.page.link/play

Welcome to Gumslinger. A gummy candy world of intense shootouts, amazing skillshots and crazy fun gunplay missions. It is a unique combination of skill, competition, physics, mouthwatering gummy candy and great fun!
